OL,3,CBrigitte Macron television drama tells
OL,4,Clove story of president and wife
OL,6,FThe romance between Brigitte Macron's
OL,7,Fand the teenage pupil who became the
OL,8,Fyoungest French president is being
OL,9,Fturned into a television series.
OL,11,FIt all began in 1992 when a 15-year-
OL,12,Fold Emmanuel Macron met Brigitte
OL,13,FAuziere, a married drama teacher 24
OL,14,Fyears his senior.
OL,16,FAfter discovering they were having an
OL,17,Faffair, Mr Macron's parents sent him
OL,18,Fto boarding school in Paris, and his
OL,19,Fteacher eventually divorced her
OL,20,Festranged husband years later in 2006.
