OL,3,CBrigitte Macron television drama tells
OL,4,Clove story of president and wife
OL,6,FIn 2007, Mr and Mrs Macron got
OL,7,Fmarried, aged 29 and 54, respectively.
OL,8,FMrs Macron has previously spoken about
OL,9,Fher anxiety surrounding their age gap.
OL,11,FIn a recent interview with Paris Match
OL,12,Fshe said her "head was a mess" and
OL,13,Ffeared that he would want to end up
OL,14,Fwith someone closer to his age.
OL,16,FShe kept teaching for a time before
OL,17,Fquitting her job in 2015 when her
OL,18,Fhusband began getting involved in
OL,19,Fpolitics - before being elected
OL,20,Fpresident in 2017.
