OL,3,CBrigitte Macron television drama tells
OL,4,Clove story of president and wife
OL,6,FProduction company Gaumont said the
OL,7,Fsix-part series, entitled Brigitte,
OL,8,Fune femme libre (Brigitte, a Free
OL,9,FWoman), will plot the romance between
OL,10,Fthe pair.
OL,12,FThe series will begin with the pair's
OL,13,Ffirst meeting and be written by French
OL,14,Fwriters Benedicte Charles and Olivier
OL,15,FPouponneau.
OL,17,FMr Charles, told Le Figaro: "Brigitte
OL,18,FMacron is a fascinating character, we
OL,19,Fwanted to approach her in a romantic,
OL,20,Falmost melodramatic way, because of
OL,21,Fthe romantic breath of her destiny."
